{"tid":924671,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"丁國琳蕾絲內衣秀F豪乳　炫耀「超透氣」！網友：逼死誰","createTime":"2018-12-02T09:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T15:00:33.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6249f598a506fcfbbf4be5ad7c737e5269d02c","tid":924671,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"這會不會太火辣了！<br />\n<br />\n本土劇女星丁國琳擁有F罩杯豪乳，年過51歲依舊亮麗火辣，堪稱演藝圈「美魔女」，她今在臉書分享自己穿著超透黑色蕾絲性感內衣的照片，大方解禁F豪乳，還透露自己穿著秀秀家的膚色「Show Bra」，讚說「超透氣，真好穿」<br />\n<br />\n雖然丁國琳不小心將「Bra」拼成「Bar」，但沒有人在意，許多網友紛紛留言「姊姊太犯規了...」「穿成這樣是要逼死誰」「假如可以跟妳交往一天！少活20年我也願意」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbPmemD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbPmemD.png&h=91c4ed99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbcf24d1150bcbe9c2336ed4e621b8ba67d5de4e","tid":924671,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"Who???"},{"pid":"32a4d0bc2223cd652a15f7f531018470a7d7b277","tid":924671,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"五十路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854efd559279c7a0ad5d27045f7b0d7af078a6de","tid":924671,"uid":147522,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"雖然丁國琳不小心將「Bra」拼成「Bar」，但沒有人在意"},{"pid":"b9558a1467295d0225f48103e02b33d7054521b6","tid":924671,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"5張幾嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77bb353f845b990de8d778675f9731f1c596054","tid":924671,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"台灣大嬸原來都係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}